Package com.OBJ2100.ExamApp.db.dao.factories

Class JdbcDaoFactory

java.lang.Object
com.OBJ2100.ExamApp.db.dao.factories.JdbcDaoFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
DaoFactory
public class JdbcDaoFactory extends Object implements DaoFactory
A JDBC-compatible implementation of the DAO factory. By implementing the DAO factory, we allow using DAOs through other media than a database. In this project, only fetching from a database is needed, meaning we do not need more implementations of the DaoFactory than the JdbcDaoFactory.
